data.description: Welcome to the gated 55 and over golfing community of Kings Gate. Spacious 1,382 square foot Sheffield home with lake and golf course view that features 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, office/den and 3 car garage. A beautifully maintained home located in a picturesque neighborhood with perfectly manicured lawns and vegetation welcomes you as soon as you approach your home.  The 3-car garage with 8’ high doors offers extra room for your vehicles, golf cart and/or storage.  As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the well-designed split floor plan, providing both privacy and functionality. The high ceilings throughout the home create an open and airy ambiance, enhancing the overall sense of spaciousness. The heart of the home is the inviting living area.  3-panel sliders open the living room up to the expanded lanai where you can relax and unwind with family and friends.  The kitchen has a nice size pantry to go along with the white cabinets and appliances (Refrigerator is excluded), Corian counters with matching backsplash, a cozy breakfast nook, also with sliders to the lanai, and tiled floor.  The master bedroom has wood laminate flooring, two walk-in closets and an attached master bath with large walk-in shower and extended vanity with his/her slink area. The guest bedroom is generously sized and provides comfortable spaces for family members or guests. The second bathroom is conveniently located, ensuring everyone's needs are met.  The den with pocket doors can be used as a third bedroom if desired.  The home also features new roof 2023, full accordion shutters all around the home for added protection, laundry in closet (washer/dryer excluded) and A/C in 2012.  Kings Gate is an active 55 and over gated community surrounded by manicured grounds with an 18-hole executive golf course.  Other great features include an Olympic size heated swimming pool and spa, tennis courts, pickle ball, lawn bowling, shuffleboard, bocce, horseshoes, gym, billiards, library and more.  If your hungry try the on-site Lion’s Den restaurant and bar.  Conveniently located next to the grocery store, drug store, bank, restaurants, shopping and I-75.
